hadiths[41]{hadithnumber,text}:
1423,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' teen tarah key log marfoo-ul-qalam hain ( yani qabil muaakhza nahin hain ( : soney wala jab tak ke neend sey bedaar na ho jaey, bachcha jab tak ke baligh na ho jaey, aur deewana jab tak ke samajh-bojh wala na ho jaey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is sanad sey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- ye hadees kaee aur sanadon sey bhi Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi hai, wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain, 3- baaz raawiyon ney (وعن الغلام حتى يحتلم) kaha hai, yani bachcha jab tak baligh na ho jaey marfoo-ul-qalam hai, 4- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key zamaney mein Hasan Basri mojud they, Hasan ney unka zamana paya hai, lekin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey unkey samaa, ka hamen ilm nahin hai, 5- ye hadees : Ata bin Saaib sey bhi marvi hai unhoney ye hadees b-tareeq : ( أبي ظبيان an علي بن أبي طالب an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) isi jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai, aur Aamash ney b-tareeq : (أبي ظبيان an ابن عباس an علي) moqufan riwayat kya hai, unhoney usey marfoo nahin kya, 6- is bab mein Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai, 7- ehle-ilm ka amal isi hadees par hai."
1424,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jahan tak tum sey ho sakey musalmanon sey hudood ko dafa karo, agar mujrim key bach nikalney ki koi surat ho to usey chhod do, kyonkey mujrim ko maaf kar deney mein Imam ka ghalati karna usey saza deney mein ghalati karney sey kahin behtar hai. is sanad sey Wakee ney Yazeed bin Ziyad sey Muhammad bin Rabeea ki hadees ki tarah bayan kya, lekin unhoney usey marfoo nahin kya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees ko hum marfoo sirf b-tareeq : (محمد بن ربيعة an يزيد بن زياد الدمشقي an الزهري an عروة an عائشة an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) hi jantey hain, 2- usey Wakee ney bhi Yazeed bin Ziyad sey isi tarah riwayat kya hai, lekin ye marfoo nahin hai, aur Wakee ki riwayat ziyada sahih hai, 3- Yazeed bin Ziyad dimashqi hadees bayan karney mein zaeef hain, aur Yazeed bin abu-Ziyad koofi un sey ziyada asbat aur aqdam hain, 4- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key kaee Sahaba sey isi tarah marvi hai, un tamam logon ney aisa hi kaha hai, 5- is bab mein Abu-Hurera aur Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1425,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney kisi momin sey duniya ki takleefon mein sey koi takleef door ki Allah uskey aakhirat ki takleefon mein sey koi takleef door kerega, aur jisney kisi musalman ki parda poshi ki to Allah duniya aur aakhirat mein uski parda-poshi farmaeyga , Allah bandey ki madad mein laga rehta hai jab tak banda apney bhai ki madad mein laga hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees pehli hadees sey ziyada sahih hai, 2- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees ko isi tarah kaee logon ney b-tareeq : (الأعمش an أبي صالح an أبي هريرة an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم), padhi. aur asbaat bin Muhammad ney Aamash sey riwayat ki hai, wo kehtey hain ke mujh sey abu-Saaleh key wastey sey bayan kya gaya hai, unhoney Abu-Hurera sey aur Abu-Hurera ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai, 3- hum sey usey Ubaid bin asbaat bin Muhammad ney bayan kya, wo kehtey hain ke mujh sey merey walid ney Aamash key wastey sey ye hadees bayan ki, 4- is bab mein Aqba bin Aamir aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1426,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' musalman musalman ka bhai hai, na is par zulm karta hai aur na uski madad chhodta hai, aur jo apney bhai ki hajat puri karney mein laga ho Allah uski hajat puri karney mein laga hota hai, jo apney kisi musalman ki pareshani door karta hai Allah uski wajeh sey us sey qiyamat ki pareshaniyon mein sey koi pareshani door kerega, aur jo kisi musalman key aeb par parda dalega Allah qiyamat key din uskey aeb par parda dalega''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
1427,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Maaiz bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : '' tumharey barey mein jo mujhey khabar mili hai kya wo sahih hai? '' Maaiz (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : merey barey mein aap ko kya khabar mili hai? aap ney farmaya : '' mujhey khabar mili hai ke tum ney falan qabiley ki londi key sath zina kya hai? '' unhoney kaha : haan, phir unhoney chaar martaba iqrar kya, to aap ney hukm diya, to unhen rajm kar diya gaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan hai, 2- is hadees ko Shoba ney Samak bin Harab sey , unhoney Saeed bin Juber sey mursalan riwayat kya hai, unhoney is sanad mein ibne-Abbas ka zikr nahin kya hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Saaib bin Yazeed sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1428,"Maaiz Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar aetraaf kya ke mainey zina kya hai, aap ney un ki taraf sey munh pher liya, phir wo dusri taraf sey aaye aur boley : Allah key Rasool! mainey zina kya hai, aap ney phir unki taraf sey munh pher liya, phir wo dusri taraf sey aaye aur boley : Allah key Rasool! mainey zina kya hai, phir chauthi martaba aetraaf karney par aap ney rajm ka hukm dey diya, chunanche wo eik pathreeli zamin ki taraf ley jaey gaey aur unhen rajm kya gaya, jab unhen pathar ki chot lagi to dodtey huye bhagey , yahan tak key eik aisey aadmi key qarib sey guzrey jis key paas oont key jabdey ki haddi thi, usney Maaiz ko usi sey maara aur logon ney bhi maara yahan tak ke wo mar gaey, phir logon ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey zikr kya ke jab pathar aur maut ki takleef unhen mehsus hui to wo bhag khadey huye they, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum logon ney isey kyon nahin chhod diya''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaee aur sanadon sey bhi marvi hai, ye hadees Zohri sey bhi marvi hai, unhoney usey b-tareeq : (عن أبي سلمة an جابر بن عبد الله an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) isi tarah riwayat ki hai) jo aagey aa rahi hai)."
1429,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein qabila Aslam key eik aadmi ney aa kar zina ka aetraaf kya, to aap ney uski taraf sey munh pher liya , phir usney iqrar kya, aap ney phir munh pher liya, yahan tak key usney khud chaar martaba iqrar kya, to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kya tum pagal ho?'' usney kaha : nahin, aap ney puchha : kya tum shaadi shuda ho? usney kaha haan : phir aap ney rajm ka hukm diya, chunanche usey eid gaah mein rajm kya gaya, jab usey patharon ney nidhal kar diya to wo bhag khada huwa, phir usey pakda gaya aur rajm kya gaya yahan tak ke wo mar gaya, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney uskey haq mein kalmaey-khair kaha lekin uski namaze-janaza nahin padhi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- baaz ehle-ilm ka amal isi par hai ke zina ka iqrar karney wala jab apney ooper chaar martaba gawahi dey to is par had qaaim ki jaeygi, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai, 3- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : eik martaba bhi koi zina ka iqrar kar lega to is par had qaaim kar di jaeygi, ye Malik bin Anas aur Shafai ka qol hai, is baat key qaailon ki daleel Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) aur Zaid bin Khalid ki ye hadees hai ke do aadmi Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tak apna qaziya ley gaey, eik ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! merey betey ney uski biwi sey zina kya, ye eik lambi hadees hai, (aakhir mein hai) Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Unais ! iski biwi key paas jaao agar wo zina ka iqrar karey to usey rajm kar do'', aap ney is hadees mein ye nahin farmaya ke '' jab chaar martaba iqrar kerey'' padhi. ."
1430,"Quraish qabila banu makhzoom ki eik aurat padhi. key mamley mein jisney chori ki thi, kafi fikrmand huye, wo kehney lagey : uskey silsiley mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kon guftgu kerega? logon ney jawab diya : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key chahetey Usama bin Zaid key ilawa kon uski jurat kar sakta hai? chunanche Usama ney aap sey baatcheet ki to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kya tum Allah ki hudood mein sey eik had key barey mein sifarish kar rahey ho? '' phir aap khadey huye aur khutba detey huye aap ney farmaya : '' logo ! tum sey pehley key log apni us rawish ki bina par halak huye ke jab koi aalaa khandan ka shakhs chori karta to usey chhod detey , aur jab kamzor haal shakhs chori karta to is par had jari kartey, Allah ki qasam! agar Muhammad ki beti Fatima chori karti to main uska (bhi) haath kaat deta ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Masood bin Ajma, ibne-Umar aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- Masood bin Ajma ko Masood bin Aajam bhi kaha jata hai, un sey sirf yehi eik hadees aai hai."
1431,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney rajm kiya, abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney rajm kiya, aur mainey bhi rajm kiya, agar main Kiitabullah mein ziyadti haram na samajhta to is ko padhi. musahaf (kitab) mein likh deta , kyonkey mujhey andesha hai ke kuchh qomen aayengi aur Kitabullah mein hukm rajm (sey mutalliq aayat) na paa kar is ka inkar kar den. Abu Eisa (Tirmizi) kehtey hain : 1- umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aur dusri sanadon sey bhi umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki gaee hai. 2- is bab mein Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1432,"Allah ney Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko haq key sath mab-us farmaya, aur aap par kitab nazil ki, aap par jo kuchh nazil kiya gaya is mein aayat rajm bhi thi padhi. , chunanche Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney rajm kiya aur aap key baad hamney bhi rajm kiya, (lekin) mujhey andesha hai ke jab logon par zamana daraz ho jaeyga to kehney waley kahengey : Allah ki kitab mein hum rajm ka hukm nahin paatey, aisey log Allah ka nazil karda eik fariza chhodney ki wajeh sey gumrah ho jaeyngey, khabrdar ! jab zaani shaadi shuda ho aur gawah mojud hon, ya jis aurat key sath zina kiya gaya ho wo hamila ho jaey, ya zaani khud aetraaf kar ley to rajm karna wajib hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aur kaee sanadon sey ye hadees umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey aai hai. 3- is bab mein Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1433,"ye log Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas mojud they, isi doran aap key paas jhagadtey huye do aadmi aaye , un mein sey eik khada huwa aur bola : Allah key Rasool ! main aap ko Allah ki qism deta hun ! aap hamarey darmiyan Kitabullah key muwaafiq faisla kijiye (ye sun kar) muddai aleh ney kaha aur wo us sey ziyada samajhdaar tha, haan , Allah key Rasool ! hamarey darmiyan aap Kitabullah key muwaafiq faisla kijiye , aur mujhey mudduaa bayan karney ki ijazat dijiye, (chunanche usney bayan kiya) mera ladka iskey paas mazdoor tha, chunanche wo iski biwi key sath zina kar betha, logon ( yani baaz ulama ( ney mujhey bataya ke merey betey par rajm wajib hai, lihaza mainey uski taraf sey sau bakri aur eik khaadim fidya mein dey di, phir meri mulaqat kuchh ehle-ilm sey hui to un logon ney kaha : merey betey par so kodey aur eik saal ki jala watni wajib hai padhi. , aur uski biwi par rajm wajib hai, (ye sun kar) Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! main tumharey darmiyan Kitabullah key muwaafiq hi faisla karunga , sau bakri aur khaadim tumhen wapis mil jaeyngey, (aur) tumharey betey ko sau kodey lagengey aur eik saal key liye usey shehar Badr kiya jaeyga, Unais ! tum uski biwi key paas jaao , agar wo zina ka aetraaf kar ley to usey rajm kar do.'' chunanche Unais uskey ghar gaey, usney jurm Qabul kar liya , lihaza unhoney usey rajm kar diya. is sanad sey Abu-Hurera aur Zaid bin Khalid Juhni sey, isi jaisi isi maana ki hadees Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat hai, is sanad sey bhi Malik ki sabiqa hadees jaisi isi maana ki hadees riwayat hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera aur Zaid bin Khalid ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isi tarah Malik bin Anas , Maamar aur kaee logon ney ba-tareeq : (الزهري ، an عبيد الله بن عتبة ، an أبي هريرة و زيد بن خالد ، an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) riwayat ki hai. 3- kuchh aur logon ney bhi isi sanad sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai, is mein hai ke ''jab laundi zina karey to usey kodey lagaao , phir agar chauthi martaba zina karey to usey bech do , chahey qeemat mein gundhey huye baalon ki rassi hi kyon na miley.''  4- aur Sufiyan bin Uena Zohri sey , Zohri Ubedullah sey , Ubedullah Abu-Hurera , Zaid bin Khalid aur Shibal Raziallahu anhum sey riwayat kartey hain, in logon ney kaha : hum log Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas mojud they. 5- ibn Uena ney isi tarah dono hadeeson ko Abu-Hurera , Zaid bin Khalid aur Shibal Raziallahu anhum sey riwayat kiya hai, ibne Uena ki hadees mein Sufiyan bin Uena sey weham huwa hai, unhoney eik hadees ko dusri hadees key sath khalat malat kar diya hai, sahih wo hadees hai jisey Muhammad bin Waleed Zubaidi , Yunus bin Ubaid aur Zohri key bhatijey ney Zohri sey , Zohri ney Ubedullah sey , Ubedullah ney Abu-Hurera aur Zaid bin Khalid sey aur in dono ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kiya hai, aap ney farmaya : ''jab laundi zina karey to usey kodey lagaao.''  6- aur Zohri ney Ubedullah sey , Ubedullah ney Shibal bin Khalid sey , Shibal ney Abdullah bin Malik Aosi sey aur unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai, aap ney farmaya : ''jab laundi zina karey.'' 7- ehale hadees key nazdik (Shibal ki riwayat ba-waste Abdullah bin Malik) yehi sahih hai, kyonkey Shibal bin Khalid ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko nahin paya hai, balke Shibal, Abdullah bin Malik Aosi sey aur wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain, yehi sahih hai aur ibne Uena ki hadees ghair mehfooz hai, kyonkey unhoney apni riwayat mein ''Shibal bin Haamid'' kaha hai, ye ghalat hai, sahih ''Shibal bin Khalid'' hai aur unhen ''Shibal bin khulaid'' bhi kaha jata hai. 8- is bab mein abu-Bakra , Ubada bin Samit , Abu-Hurera , abu-Saeed , ibne-Abbas , Jabir bin Samura , Hqazaal , Barida , Salma bin Muhbiq , abu-Barza aur Imran bin Husain (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1434,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''(deen khas tor par zina key ehkam) mujh sey seekh lo, Allah Taala ney unkey liye padhi. raah nikal di hai : shaadi shuda mard shaadi shuda aurat key sath mulawwis ho to sau kodon aur rajm ki saza hai, aur kunwaaraa kanwari key sath zina ka murtakib (mujrim) ho to sau kodon aur eik saal ki jala watni ki saza hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key baaz ehle-ilm Sahaba ka isi par amal hai, un mein Ali bin abi Talib , Ubai-bin Kaab aur Abdullah bin Masood waghera (Raziallauh anhum) shamil hain, ye log kehtey hain : shaadi shuda zaani ko kodey lagaey jaeyngey aur rajm kiya jaeyga, baaz ehle-ilm ka yehi maslak hai, Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai. 3- jabke Sahaba mein sey baaz ehle-ilm jin mein abu-Bakar aur umr waghera Raziallahu anhuma shamil hain, kehtey hain : shaadi shuda zina-kaar par sirf rajm wajib hai, usey kodey nahin lagaey jaeyngey, aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah dusri hadees mein Maaiz waghera key qisse key silsiley mein aai hai ke aap ney sirf rajm ka hukm diya, rajm sey pehley kodey laganey ka hukm nahin diya, baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Shafai aur Ahmed ka yehi qol hai."
1435,"Qabeela juhaina ki eik aurat ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas zina ka iqrar kiya, aur arz kiya : main hamila hun, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney uskey wali ko talab kiya aur farmaya : iskey sath husne-suluk karo aur jab bachcha janay to mujhey khabar karo, chunanche usney aisa hi kiya, aur phir aap ney hukm diya, chunanche uskey kapdey baandh diye gaey padhi. phir aap ney us ko rajm karney ka hukm diya, chunanche usey rajm kar diya gaya, phir aap ney uski namaze janaza padhi to umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney aap sey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! aap ney isey rajm kiya hai, phir iski namaz padh rahey hain? aap ney farmaya : ''us aurat ney aisi tauba ki hai ke agar ye Madina key sattar aadmiyon key darmiyan taqseem kar di jaey to sab ko shamil ho jaeygi padhi. , umr ! is sey achchhi koi chiz tumhari nazar mein hai ke usney Allah key liye apni jaan qurban kar di.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1436,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik Yahudi mard aur eik Yahudi aurat ko rajm kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- aur ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- hadees main eik qisse ka bhi zikr hai.
1437,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik Yahudi mard aur eik Yahudi aurat ko rajm kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar , Bara , Jabir , ibne-Abi Aufi , Abdullah bin Haris bin Juz aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo kehtey hain : jab ehale kitab aapas mein jhagden aur Muslim hukmranon key paas apna muqadma pesh karen to un par lazim hai ke wo kitab aur sunnat aur musalmanon key ehkam key mutabiq faisla karen, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai. 4- baaz log kehtey hain : ehale kitab par zina ki had na qaaim ki jaey, lekin pehla qol ziyada sahih hai."
1438,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney (ghair shaadi shuda zaani aur zaaniya ko) kodey lagaey aur shehar Badr kiya abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney bhi kodey lagaey aur shehar Badr kiya, aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney bhi kodey lagaey aur shehar Badr kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees gharib hai. 2- isey kaee logon ney Abdullah bin Idrees sey riwayat kiya hai, aur un logon ney isey marfoo kiya hai, ( jabke ( baaz logon ney is hadees ko ba-tareeq : (عن عبد الله بن إدريس هذا الحديث an عبيد الله an نافع an ابن عمر) ( moqufan ( riwayat kiya hai ke abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney ( ghair shaadi shuda zaani ko) kodey lagaey aur shehar Badr kiya, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kodey lagaey aur shehar Badr kiya. 3- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Zaid bin Khalid aur Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. hum sey isey abu-Saeed Ash'aj ney bayan kiya, wo kehtey hain ke hum sey Abdullah bin Idrees ney bayan kiya, neez (isi ke saath) isi tarah ye hadees Abdullah bin Idrees key ilawa kaee eik ney Ubedullah bin umr sey riwayat ki hai, isi tarah isey Muhammad bin Is-haq ney Nafey sey , Nafey ney ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey) moqufan ( riwayat kiya hai ke abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kodey lagaey aur shehar Badr kiya, aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kodey lagaey aur shehar Badr kiya, lekin is mein un logon ney is ka zikr nahin kiya ke ye hadees Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aai hai. 4- halanke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi shehar Badr karney ki riwayat sahih hai. 5- isey Abu-Hurera , Zaid bin Khalid aur Ubada bin Samit waghera (Raziallauh anhum) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kiya hai. 6- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key Sahaba mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka amal isi par hai, in logon mein abu-Bakar , umr , Ali , Ubai-bin Kaab , Abdullah bin Masood aur Abu-Zar waghaira (Raziallauh anhum) shamil hain, isi tarah ye hadees kaee Tabe-een fuqaha sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai, Sufiyan Sory Malik bin Anas , Abdullah bin Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai."
1439,"Hum log Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik majlis mein mojud they, aap ney farmaya : ''hum sey is baat par baiat karo ke tum Allah key sath shirk na karogey, chori na karogey aur zina na karogey, phir aap ney unkey samney aayat padhi padhi. aur farmaya : jo is iqrar ko pura karega uska ajr Allah key zimme hai aur jo in mein sey kisi gunah ka murtakib (mujrim) huwa phir is par had qaaim ho gaee to ye uskey liye kaffara ho jaeyga padhi. , aur jisney koi gunah kiya aur Allah ney is par parda dal diya to wo Allah key ikhtiyar mein hai, chahey to usey azab dey aur chahey to usey bakhsh dey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ubada bin Samit ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Imam Shafai kehtey hain : mainey is baab mein is hadees sey achchhi koi chiz nahin suni ke hudood as-haabe-hudood key liye kaffara hain. 3- Shafai kehtey hain : main chahta hun ke jab koi gunah karey aur Allah is par parda dal dey to wo khud apney ooper parda dal ley aur apney us gunah ki aisi tauba karey ke usey aur uskey rab key siwa kisi ko uska ilm na ho. 4- abu-Bakar aur umr Raziallahu anhuma sey isi tarah marvi hai ke unhoney eik aadmi ko hukm diya ke wo apney ooper parda dal ley. 5- is bab mein Ali , Jareer bin Abdullah aur Khuzaima bin Sabit (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1440,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum mein sey kisi ki laundi zina karey to Allah ki kitab key (hukm key) mutabiq teen baar usey kodey lagao padhi. agar wo phir bhi (yani chauthi baar) zina karey to usey farokht kar do , chahey qeemat mein baal ki rassi hi miley.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- in sey ye hadees kaee sanadon sey aai hai. 3- is bab mein Ali , Abu-Hurera , Zaid bin Khalid (Raziallauh anhum) sey aur Shibal sey ba-waste Abdullah bin Malik Aosi bhi hadeesen aai hain. 4- Sahaba mein sey baaz ehle-ilm aur kuchh doosrey logon ka isi par amal hai, ye log kehtey hain ke haakim key bajaey aadmi apney mamlook (ghulam) par khud had nafiz karey, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai. 5- baaz log kehtey hain : Haakim key paas muqadma pesh kiya jaeyga, koi aadmi b-zaate-khud had nafiz nahin karega, lekin pehla qol ziyada sahih hai."
1441,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney khutbe key doran kaha : logo ! apney ghulamon aur laundiyon par had qaaim karo, jiski shaadi hui ho is par bhi aur jiski shaadi na hui ho is par bhi, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki eik laundi ney zina kiya, chunanche aap ney mujhey kodey laganey ka hukm diya, main uskey paas aaya to (dekha) us ko kuchh hi din pehley nifaas ka khoon aaya tha padhi. lihaza mujhey andesha huwa ke agar mainey isey kodey lagaey to kahin main isey qatl na kar bethun , ya unhoney kaha : kahin wo mar na jaey padhi. , chunanche main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas gaya aur aap sey usey bayan kiya, to aap ney farmaya : '' tum ney achchha kiya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1442,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney had qaaim kartey huye chaalis jootiyon ki saza di, Musa'ir Raavi kehtey hain : mera khayal hai sharab ki had mein (aap ney chaalis jootiyon ki saza di). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein Ali , Abdur-Rehman bin Azhar , Abu-Hurera , Saaib , ibne-Abbas aur Aqba bin Haris (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1443,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik aisa aadmi laya gaya jisney sharab pi thi, aap ney isey khajoor ki do chhadiyon sey chaalis key qarib maara , abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney bhi (apney daure khilaafat mein) aisa hi kiya, phir jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) khalifa huye to unhoney is silsiley mein logon sey mashwara kiya, chunanche Abdur-Rehman bin Auf ney kaha : hadon mein sab sey halki had assi kodey hain, chunanche umr ney assi ka hukm diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Sahaba mein sey ehle-ilm aur doosrey logon ka isi par amal hai ke shraabi ki had assi kodey hain."
1444,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo sharab piye usey kodey lagaao , phir agar chauthi baar piey to usey qatl kar do.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees ko isi tarah Sory ney ba-tareeq : (Aasim an abi Saleh an Muawiya an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat kiya hai, aur ibne-Jurej aur Maamar ney ba-tareeq : (Suhail bin abi Saleh an Abeeh an abi Huraira an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat kiya hai. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey huye suna hai ke abu-Saaleh ki hadees jo ba-waste Muawiya Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey is silsiley mein aai hai, ye abu-Saaleh ki is hadees sey jo ba-waste Abu-Hurera Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aai hai ziyada sahih hai. 3- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Shareed , Shurehbil bin Aus , Jareer , Abu Ramad Balwi aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 4- ye hukm ibtidaa Islam mein tha padhi. phir uskey baad mansookh ho gaya, isi tarah Muhammad bin Is-haq ney ''(Muhammad bin Munkadar an Jabir bin Abdullah) key tareeq sey riwayat ki hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ne farmaya : ''jo sharab piye usey kodey lagaao, phir agar chauthi baar piye to usey qatl kar do.''  phir iskey baad Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik aisa aadmi laya gaya jisney chauthi baar sharab pi thi, to aap ney isey kodey lagaey aur qatl nahin kiya, isi tarah Zohri ney Qabisa bin Zuweb sey aur unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai. 5- chunanche qatl ka hukm mansookh ho gaya, pehley iski rukhsat thi, aam ehle-ilm ka usi hadees par amal hai, merey ilm mein is masle mein unkey darmiyan na pehley ikhtilaf tha na ab ikhtilaf hai, aur iski taeed is riwayat sey bhi hoti hai jo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey beshumaar sanadon sey aai hai ke aap ney farmaya : jo musalman shahadat deta ho ke Allah key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin aur main Allah ka Rasool hun to uska khoon teen mein sey kisi eik chiz ki bina par hi halal ho sakta hai : nahaq kisi ka qatil ho, shaadi shuda zaani ho, ya apna Deen (Islam) chhodney wala (murtad) ho.''"
1445,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam chothai Dinar padhi. aur is sey ziyada ki chori par haath kaat'tey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees dusri sanadon sey Umra key wastey sey Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey marfooan aai hai, jabke baaz logon ney isey Umra key wastey sey Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey moqufan riwayat kiya hai."
1446,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik dhaal ki chori par haath kaataa jiski qeemat teen dirham padhi. thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Saad , Abdullah bin Amr , ibne-Abbas , Abu-Hurera aur Aiman (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sahaba mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, un mein abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi shamil hain, unhoney paanch dirham ki chori par haath kaataa. 4- Usman aur Ali Raziallahu anhuma sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke un logon ney chothai Dinar ki chori par haath kaataa. 5- Abu-Hurera aur abu Saeed Khudri Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain ke paanch dirham ki chori par haath kaataa jaeyga. 6- baaz faqeeho aur Tabe-een ka isi par amal hai, Malik bin Anas , Shafai , Ahmed , Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai, ye log kehtey hain : chothai Dinar aur is sey ziyada ki chori par haath kaataa jaeyga. 7- aur ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke eik Dinar ya das dirham ki chori par hi haath kaataa jaeyga, lekin ye mursal (yani munqata') hadees hai isey Qasim bin Abdur-Rehman ney ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kiya hai, halanke Qasim ney ibne-Masood sey nahin suna hai, baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, chunanche Sufiyan Sory aur ehle-koofa ka yehi qol hai, ye log kehtey hain : das dirham sey kam ki chori par haath na kaataa jaey. 8- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke das dirham sey kam ki chori par haath nahin kaataa jaeyga, lekin iski sanad muttasil nahin hai."
1447,"Mainey Fazala bin Ubaid sey puchha : kya chor ka haath kaatney key baad uski gardan mein latkana sunnat hai? unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik chor laya gaya uska haath kaataa gaya, phir aap ney hukm diya haath uski gardan mein latka diya gaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf umr bin Ali Muqaddami hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain, unhoney isey Hujjaaj bin Irtaat sey riwayat kiya hai."
1448,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' khayanat karney waley,daaku aur uchakke  ki saza haath kaatna nahin hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Mughira bin Muslim ney ibne-Jurej ki hadees ki tarah isey abu-Zubair sey , abu-Zubair ney Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey aur Jabir ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kiya hai. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai."
1449,Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''phal aur khajoor key gaabhey ki chori mein haath nahin kaataa jaeyga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- isi tarah baaz aur logon ney bhi Les bin Saad ki riwayat ki tarah ba-tareeq : (يحيى بن سعيد an محمد بن يحيى بن حبان an عمه واسع بن حبان an رافع بن خديج an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) riwayat ki hai. 2- Malik bin Anas aur kaee logon ney is hadees ko ba-tareeq : (يحيى بن سعيد an محمد بن يحيى بن حبان an رافع بن خديج an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) riwayat kya hai. un logon ney is hadees ki sanad mein Waasey bin Hibban ka zikr nahin kiya.
1450,"Mainey Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : ''jang key doran (chori karney waley ka ( haath nahin kaataa jaeyga.''Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- ibne-Lahiaa key ilawa kuchh doosrey logon ney bhi isi sanad sey isi jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, unhi mein Auzaai bhi hain, ye log kehtey hain : dushman ki mojudgi mein jihad key doran (chori karney par) had qaaim nahin ki jaeygi, kyonkey jis par had qaaim ki jaeygi andesha hai ke wo dushman sey mil jaey, albatta Imam jab Darul-harab sey nikal kar Darul-Islam wapis aa jaey to chori karney waley par had qaaim karey."
1451,"Noman bin Bashir Raziallahu anhuma key paas eik aisey shakhs ka muqadma pesh huwa jisney apni biwi ki laundi key sath zina kiya tha, unhoney kaha : main is mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key faisle key mutabiq faisla karunga : agar uski biwi ney isey laundi key sath jima (sambhog) ki ijazat di hai to (bator had) isey sau kodey maaroonga aur agar usney ijazat nahin di hai to (bator had) isey rajm (sangsaar) karunga."
1452,"Noman bin Bashir sey usi jaisi hadees aai hai. Qatada kehtey hain ke unhoney kaha : Habib bin Salim key paas ye masla likh kar bheja gaya. abu-Bashar ney bhi ye hadees Habib bin Salim sey nahin suni , unhoney isey Khalid bin Arfata sey riwayat kiya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Noman ki hadees ki sanad mein iztirab (ikhtilaaf) hai mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna ke Qatada ney is hadees ko Habib bin Salim sey nahin suna hai, unhoney isey Khalid bin Arfataa sey riwayat kiya hai. 2- is bab mein Salma bin Muhbiq sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- biwi ki laundi key sath zina karney waley key silsiley mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai, chunanche Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key kaee Sahaba sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai jin mein Ali aur ibne-Umar bhi shamil hain ke is par rajm wajib hai, ibne-Masood kehtey hain is par koi had nahin hai, albatta uski islaahi saza hogi , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka maslak is ( hadees ( key mutabiq hai jo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ba-wasta Noman bin Bashir aai hai."
1453,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamaney main eik aurat key sath zabardasti zina kiya gaya, to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney isey had sey bari kar diya aur zaani par had jari ki. Raavi ney is ka zikr nahin kiya ke aap ney isey kuchh mehar bhi dilaaya ho. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, iski asnaad muttasil nahin hai. 2- ye hadees dusri sanad sey bhi aai hai. 3- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey huye suna : Abdul-Jabbaar bin Wayl bin Hajar ka samaa, unkey baap sey sabit nahin hai, unhoney apney walid ka zamana nahin paya hai, kaha jata hai ke wo apney walid ki maut key kuchh mahiney baad paida huye. 4- Sahaba kiram mein sey baaz ehle-ilm aur kuchh doosrey logon ka isi par amal hai ke jis sey jabran zina kiya gaya ho is par had wajib nahin hai."
1454,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamaney main eik aurat namaz key liye nikli, usey eik aadmi mila , usney aurat ko dhanp liya aur us sey apni hajat puri ki (yani us sey zabardasti zina kiya), wo aurat cheekhney lagi aur wo chala gaya, phir uskey paas sey eik (doosra) aadmi guzra to ye aurat boli : is (doosray) aadmi ney merey sath aisa-aisa (yani zina) kiya hai padhi. aur uskey paas sey muhajrin ki bhi eik jamaat guzri to ye aurat boli : is aadmi ney merey sath aisa aisa (yani zina) kiya hai, ( ye sun kar) wo log gaey aur ja kar unhoney us aadmi ko pakad liya jis key barey mein us aurat ney guman kiya tha ke usi ney uskey sath zina kiya hai aur usey is aurat key paas laye, wo boli : haan , wo yehi hai, phir wo log usey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas laye, chunanche jab aap ney isey rajm karney ka hukm diya, to us aurat key sath zina karney wala khada huwa aur usney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! uskey sath zina karney wala main hun, phir aap ney us aurat sey farmaya : ''tu ja Allah ney teri bakhshish kar di hai.'' aur aap ney us aadmi ko (jo qasurwaar nahin tha) achchhi baat kahi padhi. aur jis aadmi ney zina kiya tha uskey mutalliq aap ney farmaya : ''usey rajm karo''  aap ney ye bhi farmaya : ''us (zaani) ney aisi tauba ki hai ke agar ehale Madina is tarah tauba kar lein to un sab ki tauba qubul ho jaey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai. 2- Alqama bin Wayl bin Hajar ka samaa (sun'na), unkey walid sey Sabit hai, ye Abdul-Jabbaar bin Wayl sey badey hain aur Abdul-Jabbaar ka samaa, unkey walid sey sabit nahin."
1455,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jis aadmi ko janwer key sath wati (sambhog) kartey huye paao to usey qatl kar do aur (sath mein) janwer ko bhi qatl kar do.'' Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey puchha gaya : janwer ko qatl karney ki kya wajeh hai? unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey is silsiley mein kuchh nahin suna hai, lekin mera khayal hai ke jis janwer key sath ye bura kaam kiya gaya ho, uska gosht khaney aur us sey faeyda uthaney ko Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney napasand samjha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Amr bin abi Amr ki hadees ko jisey wo ba-tareeq : (Akrama an ibne-Abbas an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat kartey hain. hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
1456,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum log jisey qome-Loot ka amal (ighlaam-bazi) kartey huye paao to faail (karta) aur mafool (karm) (bura kaam karney aur karaney waley) dono ko qatl kar do. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees ba-wasta ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey sirf isi sanad sey jaani jati hai, Muhammad bin Is-haq ney bhi is hadees ko Amr bin abi Amr sey riwayat kiya hai, (lekin is mein hai) aap ney farmaya : ''qome-Loot ka amal (ighlaam-bazi) karney wala maloon hai.''  Raavi ney is hadees mein qatl ka zikr nahin kiya, albatta is mein ye bayan hai ke janwer sey wati (sambhog) karney wala maloon hai.''  aur ye hadees ba-tareeq : Aasim bin umr an Suhail bin Abi Saleh an Abeeh an Abi Huraira an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat ki gaee hai. (is mein hai ke) aap ney farmaya : ''faail (karm) aur mafool (karta) dono ko qatl kar do.''  2- is hadees ki sanad mein kalam hai, hum nahin jantey ke isey Suhel bin abi Saleh sey Aasim bin umr Al Umri key ilawa kisi aur ney riwayat kiya hai aur Aasim bin umr ka haal ye hai ke wo apney hifz key talluq sey hadees bayan karney mein zaeef hain. 3- is bab mein Jabir aur Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 4- ighlaam-bazi (bura kaam) karney waley ki had key silsiley mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai, baaz kehtey hain : bura kaam karney wala shaadi shuda ho ya ghair shaadi shuda uski saza rajm hai, Malik Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai. 5- Fuqaha Tabe-een mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ney jin mein Hasan Basri , Ibrahim Nakhai aur Ata bin abi Ribah waghera shamil hain kehtey hain : bura kaam karney waley ki saza zaani ki saza ki tarah hai, Sory aur ehle-Koofa ka yehi qol hai."
1457,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' mujhey apni ummat key barey mein jis chiz ka sab sey ziyada khof hai wo qome-Loot ka amal (ighlaam-bazi) hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- aur hum isey sirf isi sanad « an Abdullah bin Muhammad bin Aqeel bin abi Talib an Jabir » sey hi jantey hain.
1458,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney kuchh aisey logon ko zinda jala diya jo Islam sey murtad ho gaey they, jab ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ko ye baat malum hui padhi. to unhoney kaha : agar (Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki jagah) main hota to unhen qatl karta , kyonkey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka farman hai : ''jo apney Deen (Islam) ko badal daley usey qatl karo.'' , aur main unhen jalata nahin kyonkey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka farman hai : ''Allah key azabe-khaas jaisa tum log azab na do.'' , phir is baat ki khabar Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko hui to unhoney kaha : ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney sach kaha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih Hasan hai. 2- murtad key silsiley mein ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. 3- jab aurat Islam sey murtad ho jaey to uskey barey mein ulama ka ikhtilaf hai, ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat kehti hai : usey qatl kya jaeyga, Auzaai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai. 4- aur ehle-ilm ki dusri jamaat kehti hai : usey qatl nahin balke qaid kiya jaeyga, Sufiyan Sory aur unkey ilawa baaz ehle-Koofa ka yehi qol hai."
1459,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo hamarey khilaf hathiyar uthaey wo hum mein sey nahin hai.'' is baab mein ibne-Umar , ibn Zuber , Abu-Hurera aur Salma bin Akwaa (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1460,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jadugar ki saza talwaar sey gardan maarna hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai, aur sahih ye hai ke Jundub sey moqufan marvi hai. 2- hum is hadees ko sirf isi sanad sey marfoo jantey hain. 3- Ismail bin Muslim Makki apney hifz key talluq sey hadees bayan karney mein zaeef hain, aur Ismail bin Muslim jinki nisbat Abdi aur Basraa hai Wakee ney unhen bharosemand kaha hai. 4- Sahaba kiram mein sey baaz ehle-ilm Sahaba aur kuchh doosrey logon ka isi par amal hai, Malik bin Anas ka yehi qol hai. 5- Shafai kehtey hain : jab jadugar ka jadu kufr ki had tak pahunchey to usey qatl kiya jaeyga aur jab uska jadu hade-kufr tak na pahunchey to hum samajhtey hain ke uska qatl nahin hai."
1461,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jis shakhs ko Allah ki raah mein maal (ghanimat) mein khayanat kartey huye paao uska saman jala do.'' Saleh kehtey hain : main Muslima key paas gaya, unkey sath Salim bin Abdullah they to Muslima ney eik aisey aadmi ko paya jisney maale-ghanimat mein khayanat ki thi, chunanche Salim ney ( un sey) ye hadees bayan ki, to Muslima ney hukm diya phir us ( khaain (ka saman jala diya gaya aur uskey saman main eik mushaf (kitab) bhi paya gaya to Salim ney kaha : isey bech do aur iski qeemat sadqa kar do. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is hadees key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : isey Saleh bin Muhammad bin zyada ney riwayat kiya hai, yehi abu Waqid Laisi hai, ye hadees ke munkir hai. 3- Bukhari kehtey hain ke maale ghanimat mein khayanat karney waley key silsiley mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey dusri ahadees bhi aai hain, aap ney un mein is (khaain) key saman jalane ka hukm nahin diya hai. 4- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, Auzaai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai."
1462,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab koi aadmi doosrey ko Yahudi keh kar pukarey to usey bees kodey lagaao , aur jab mukhannas (hijdaa) keh kar pukarey to usey bees kodey lagaao , aur jo kisi mohrim (aehraam ki haalat me) key sath zina karey usey qatl kar do.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- hum is hadees ko sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- Ibrahim bin Ismail bin Aleh hadees ki riwayat mein zaeef hain. 3- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye kaee sanadon sey marvi hai. 4- Bara bin Aazib aur Qurra bin Ayas Muzni sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney apney baap ki biwi sey nikah kiya to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney usey qatl karney ka hukm diya. 5- hamarey as-haab (muhaddeseen) ka isi par amal hai, ye log kehtey hain : jo jantey huye kisi mohrim key sath zina karey to is par qatl wajib hai. 6- (Imam) Ahmed kehtey hain : jo apni maa sey nikah karega usey qatl kya jaeyga. 7- Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain : jo kisi mohrim key sath zina karey usey qatl kiya jaeyga."
1463,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam farmaya : '' das sey ziyada kisi ko kodey na lagaey jaeyn padhi. siwaye uskey ke Allah ki hudood mein sey koi had jari karna ho.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Bakeer bin Ashajj ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- saza key silsiley mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai, saza key baab mein ye hadees sab sey achchhi hai. 3- is hadees ko ibne-Lahiaa ney Bakeer sey riwayat kiya hai, lekin un sey is sanad mein ghalati hui hai, unhoney sanad is tarah bayan ki hai : « an Abdur-Rehman bin Jabir bin Abdullah an Abeeh an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » halanke ye ghalat hai, sahih Les bin Saad ki hadees hai, iski sanad is tarah hai : (عبدالرحمٰن بن جابر بن عبد الله an أبي بردة بن نيار an النبِ صلى الله عليه وسلم)."
